00:13:27,703 --> 00:13:29,291
- Briefcase, Briefcase.

275
00:13:29,429 --> 00:13:32,052
[somber music]

276
00:13:34,089 --> 00:13:36,056
[monitor beeping]

277
00:13:36,194 --> 00:13:38,162
[Briefcase snores]

278
00:13:38,300 --> 00:13:41,751
[Briefcase gasping]

279
00:13:41,890 --> 00:13:44,306
- Hey, hey, take it easy now.

