311
00:15:06,146 --> 00:15:07,699
- Is that a joke?

312
00:15:07,837 --> 00:15:09,287
'Cause if you're joking,

313
00:15:09,425 --> 00:15:11,669
you better work on your
bedside manner, Preacher.

314
00:15:13,326 --> 00:15:15,535
Are you joking or are you
just trying to trick me?

315
00:15:15,673 --> 00:15:18,262
- We're not the Mayo
Clinic, we could be wrong.

316
00:15:18,400 --> 00:15:19,573
Maybe you'll live 10 years

317
00:15:19,711 --> 00:15:21,161
