you expect to live

323
00:15:29,135 --> 00:15:30,999
the way you were living,
and not have a bad--

324
00:15:31,137 --> 00:15:32,690
- I don't need you
preaching at me.

325
00:15:35,796 --> 00:15:36,487
I'm sorry.

326
00:15:37,937 --> 00:15:39,076
I'm sorry, but

327
00:15:40,940 --> 00:15:45,392
what I meant was, this is a
lot to take in in five minutes.

328
00:15:46,876 --> 00:15:48,085
I just wanna be alone.

329
00:15:49,845 --> 00:15:50,880
[gentle music]

330
00:15:51,019 --> 00:15:52,296
