333
00:16:09,934 --> 00:16:12,592
[chips crunching]

334
00:16:14,801 --> 00:16:17,700
- [Clerk] Rummie,
how you doing today?

335
00:16:17,838 --> 00:16:19,944
- Can't believe it, it's
like I'm on autopilot.

336
00:16:20,082 --> 00:16:22,740
- You know I was just reading
about you in the newspaper.

337
00:16:22,878 --> 00:16:25,329
Did you know that 10%
of the boozers out there

