all the alcohol sales.

339
00:16:28,953 --> 00:16:31,680
- You're full of all sorts of
fun facts today, aren't ya?

340
00:16:31,818 --> 00:16:34,717
- [Clerk] Hey, if it wasn't for
you, I'd be out of business.

341
00:16:34,855 --> 00:16:35,649
What'll it be today?

342
00:16:37,720 --> 00:16:39,791
- Is this stuff supposed
to be good for ya?

343
00:16:41,310 --> 00:16:43,105
