of the jerky family.

344
00:16:43,243 --> 00:16:45,832
99% fat free.

345
00:16:45,970 --> 00:16:47,903
But Olympians don't train on it.

346
00:16:48,041 --> 00:16:50,078
- Well, I'll take one.

347
00:16:51,493 --> 00:16:53,081
- And?

348
00:16:53,219 --> 00:16:58,189
- And, hey two years
is a long time,

349
00:16:59,328 --> 00:17:00,536
wouldn't you say?

350
00:17:02,021 --> 00:17:04,368
- [laughs] Yeah, especially
if somebody is poking ya

