00:17:35,502 --> 00:17:36,814
- Hey, look what is this?

366
00:17:36,952 --> 00:17:38,609
Can't a guy buy a pinwheel?

367
00:17:38,747 --> 00:17:40,404
- I'm willing to go along
with you on the jerky thing,

368
00:17:40,542 --> 00:17:41,819
'cause a man's gotta eat.

369
00:17:41,957 --> 00:17:43,821
But the rest of the
10% of the boozers

