disappointed in you, Rummie.

371
00:17:46,858 --> 00:17:48,791
You're not maximizing your
alcohol purchase here.

372
00:17:48,929 --> 00:17:50,690
- Look, just ring me up.

373
00:17:52,243 --> 00:17:53,072
- Okay.

374
00:17:57,110 --> 00:17:58,077
Change.

375
00:18:00,251 --> 00:18:01,149
- Thanks a lot.

376
00:18:05,222 --> 00:18:07,016
- Briefcase, I'm
telling you, [laughs]

377
00:18:07,155 --> 00:18:09,018
you really scared me there.

378
00:18:09,157 --> 00:18:11,987
- Who needs extreme sports
