404
00:19:23,645 --> 00:19:25,854
- It looks kinda lame to me.

405
00:19:27,787 --> 00:19:28,650
- Oh.

406
00:19:30,065 --> 00:19:31,515
Well, well, you know
Santa always gives

407
00:19:31,653 --> 00:19:33,344
