408
00:19:33,482 --> 00:19:34,863
but you know, they get better.

409
00:19:36,002 --> 00:19:37,383
Here, why don't
you give it a try.

410
00:19:37,521 --> 00:19:39,385
[bright music]

411
00:19:39,523 --> 00:19:41,559
Well, get up and
move around with it.

412
00:19:41,697 --> 00:19:42,526
Yeah.

413
00:19:44,804 --> 00:19:46,081
Back and forth.

