- Look, this ain't
Bank of America,

474
00:22:31,557 --> 00:22:33,006
you gotta buy something.

475
00:22:33,144 --> 00:22:35,699
- Look, I just need the
money, okay, please.

476
00:22:35,837 --> 00:22:38,149
- How about this bottle of rum?

477
00:22:38,287 --> 00:22:39,599
Ronrico, huh.

